item.title: Mystery Solved! Not an Alien Base! Not Atlantean Pyramids!
item.dc:creator: themeauthor@thememattic.com
item.content:encoded:
Location:   Antarctica

Coordinates: -75.012136, 0.067692
item.excerpt:encoded: There has been much speculation about this mysterious structure in Antarctica. People in Youtube videos have been measuring distances between those visible repeating mounds or whatever they are, proving that this is not a natural formation. Then, these people concluded, it must be remnants of an ancient civilization or an alien base. Some even suggested that the hole on the left is an entrance into an underground hidden space! A simple look at the list of research installations in Antarctica proved this elegant theory false. This is not a natural formation, check! The pattern is there, check! But this is manmade! This is nothing but a German summer-only research station. It is called Kohnen Station and you can read more about it here. Sorry to disappoint, conspiracy theorists!
item.wp:post_name: Mystery Solved! Not an Alien Base! Not Atlantean Pyramids!

I am including the screenshots, as the maps will lose even the low resolution Gulliver pretty soon. There is a Flikr page with more info.
